All the Bangladeshi friends claiming this song as their own will do well to remember that their national anthem was written by an Indian- Rabindranath Tagore. So Indians are well within their rights to claim "Amar Sonar Bangla" as an Indian song. So please stop this business of claiming songs and just enjoy the music. 
Thank you.
